<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08193</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT CREATING THE NATIONAL ROAD SAFETY BOARD AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to address the alarming number of road crash-related deaths in the country which calls for immediate countermeasures in order to curb such increasing leading cause of deaths.

Calls for the creation of a road safety board responsible for synthesizing all these countermeasures.
